WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.533 --> 00:00:02.766
Xiaoshuang, how much did you say just now?

2
00:00:02.866 --> 00:00:05.033
The 1 million in this box

3
00:00:05.966 --> 00:00:07.366
You little brat

4
00:00:07.366 --> 00:00:09.666
Don't say you bet on 1 million

5
00:00:09.733 --> 00:00:11.800
Even if you bet 10 million

6
00:00:12.266 --> 00:00:14.466
I won't spend a penny of your gambling money

7
00:00:14.466 --> 00:00:16.266
Mom, you misunderstood.

8
00:00:16.266 --> 00:00:17.766
I didn't gamble the money

9
00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:19.266
I helped my sister make money in the stock market

10
00:00:19.266 --> 00:00:20.300
If you don't believe me, ask her.

11
00:00:20.366 --> 00:00:22.966
It's Auntie, I'm here, Mom.

12
00:00:22.966 --> 00:00:24.833
You can't blame it all together.

13
00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:27.866
It's my own illness that's holding you back

14
00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:29.366
Put you in so much debt

15
00:00:29.400 --> 00:00:30.200
Xiaoyan

16
00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:33.366
It's our family that's sorry for your parents

17
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:34.600
Marry into our family

18
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:37.233
Never had a comfortable day

19
00:00:37.333 --> 00:00:39.966
You have to earn money to support your family and raise your children

20
00:00:40.166 --> 00:00:41.633
Marry into our family

21
00:00:41.766 --> 00:00:44.033
You're in a fire pit

22
00:00:44.666 --> 00:00:48.066
Mom, we won't mention the past

23
00:00:48.066 --> 00:00:51.966
I believe it will get better and better in the future.

24
00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:55.466
Mom Xiaoyan is right

25
00:00:55.566 --> 00:00:56.766
I will try my best in the future.

26
00:00:56.766 --> 00:00:58.900
Will definitely make you live a happier life

27
00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.566
Son's mother doesn't expect you to be rich

28
00:01:03.566 --> 00:01:06.666
I just hope you can be an upright man

29
00:01:06.666 --> 00:01:08.300
Can be looked up to

30
00:01:08.333 --> 00:01:09.766
And you know what?

31
00:01:11.066 --> 00:01:12.100
I see, Mom.

32
00:01:13.066 --> 00:01:14.833
Mom last life

33
00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:16.500
I thought I was in gambling debt

34
00:01:16.533 --> 00:01:17.500
I'm afraid you'll throw it in

35
00:01:17.700 --> 00:01:20.733
In this life, I will make all the relatives who laugh at you

36
00:01:20.733 --> 00:01:22.533
They all look up to your family to be rich

37
00:01:22.533 --> 00:01:23.766
I don't want the money today.

38
00:01:23.766 --> 00:01:25.366
We're staying here

39
00:01:25.366 --> 00:01:27.466
Walk around his second aunt and second uncle

40
00:01:27.466 --> 00:01:29.233
You also came to see Xiaoyan, right?

41
00:01:30.566 --> 00:01:34.033
Who sees the sick children in your house? Pay back the money.

